name: getfeedversions
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool transitfeeds.
Tool description: An extensive collection of official public transit data from around the world, including GTFS, GTFS-RealTime and more.
API description: Retrieve a list of feed versions from the TransitFeeds API, optionally filtering the results based on the given parameters.

feed.description: The feed ID to restrict results to. Defaults to 'sfmta/60'.

page.description: The page of results to return. If None, the first page is returned.
